---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 430
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Heterodoxy And Deviation=‘And Ye Shall Be as Gods’
  - 579
By: Ananda Moyi
---
To acquire the power to attain the Infinite, one must first know the
finite and let oneself be guided by it. As long as the soul is
identified with the body, it is indispensable to let oneself be guided
by what the rules enjoin or proscribe.
